                    <comment id="12661241" author="ryantxu" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2009 18:32:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Any chance you could make a new patch without SerialChainFilter moved to search?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should we make a new package for geohash based things?&lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.lucene.spatial.geohash&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
